title: Logitech MK520 Keyboard and Mouse | REVIEW |
description:
Hey Everyone!  

This is my review of the Logitech MK520 Keyboard and Mouse Combo. This is an extremely affordable and great quality set of peripherals for any desk setup be it productivity or gaming. 

I hope you guys like the video, please comment if you have any suggestions on how I should conduct future reviews and subscribe if you loved it!

Filmed on the iPhone 6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Amazon Link: https://www.amazon.com/LogitechMk520-Wireless-Keyboard-Mouse-Combo/dp/B003VANO7C/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1475605077&sr=8-1&keywords=mk520
